{"id": "ChIJA9tWxYbFwoARKooI8X8JsWU", "rating": 4.8, "userRatingCount": 19, "displayName": {"text": "灵韵奶趣 Lingyun Milk Fun", "languageCode": "zh"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJA9tWxYbFwoARKooI8X8JsWU/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xwS1kyNVpRWGx6UWxKQ1YwbzRZV1ppTlU1TlJHYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I ordered on Fantuan last week and today I visited in person for the first time. The shop is in the corner and a bit obscure, I hope they do a better advertisement bc the yogurt is so good! The dry yogurt is a bit pricey, but I went in person and saw lots of fresh fruits in the fridge, so it’s really just the high quality ingredients they use. I’ve been using the dry yogurt as spreads on my toast for breakfast and I look forward to trying a new flavor every time, every option is so delicious and on point so far and I love how many flavors they have!!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I ordered on Fantuan last week and today I visited in person for the first time. The shop is in the corner and a bit obscure, I hope they do a better advertisement bc the yogurt is so good! The dry yogurt is a bit pricey, but I went in person and saw lots of fresh fruits in the fridge, so it’s really just the high quality ingredients they use. I’ve been using the dry yogurt as spreads on my toast for breakfast and I look forward to trying a new flavor every time, every option is so delicious and on point so far and I love how many flavors they have!!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Yun Chiu", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102451782279117072334/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWbH_ajc1wci829xW8D_lWgBdTPyPnRMHW1JoFHXUe57HeGHeDk=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-25T04:58:34.476858760Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xwS1kyNVpRWGx6UWxKQ1YwbzRZV1ppTlU1TlJHYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xwS1kyNVpRWGx6UWxKQ1YwbzRZV1ppTlU1TlJHYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c586c556db03:0x65b1097ff1088a2a"}, {"name": "places/ChIJA9tWxYbFwoARKooI8X8JsWU/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xKM1VYWXRPVTV0TjBKS00weFBSa000VVhKbk0xRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Interesting dessert option….wasn’t sure what to expect but it ended up being yummy! We tried the dry mango yogurt and it had a similar taste to mango lassi. It is very dry though so small bites! We also had the Lychee Yogurt Purple Rice Drink which was delicious, will be back for that! Interestingly it is not cold, they don’t blend with ice but it didn’t bother us. (maybe because the weather is cold right now)", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Interesting dessert option….wasn’t sure what to expect but it ended up being yummy! We tried the dry mango yogurt and it had a similar taste to mango lassi. It is very dry though so small bites! We also had the Lychee Yogurt Purple Rice Drink which was delicious, will be back for that! Interestingly it is not cold, they don’t blend with ice but it didn’t bother us. (maybe because the weather is cold right now)", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Garrett Mason", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110059857239202722574/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIRAd8LiSkACJ7D06h2DQGAOliAHsPzERD8eQhHg90A4Z6r9A=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-21T04:40:33.321209886Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xKM1VYWXRPVTV0TjBKS00weFBSa000VVhKbk0xRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xKM1VYWXRPVTV0TjBKS00weFBSa000VVhKbk0xRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c586c556db03:0x65b1097ff1088a2a"}, {"name": "places/ChIJA9tWxYbFwoARKooI8X8JsWU/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xOUlJFTlNhRmxvWDNaVmRWZGZWMjlwUTFrd2QyYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Love! Good service, yummy yogurt, fruits are always fresh and high quality!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Love! Good service, yummy yogurt, fruits are always fresh and high quality!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Didi Uchiha", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105890109091986425269/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIsEUqa1T2-O8dToUlJwzW7goNxhqRPW02wIlk8o9rt9_KLWg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-05T04:51:38.819116954Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xOUlJFTlNhRmxvWDNaVmRWZGZWMjlwUTFrd2QyYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xOUlJFTlNhRmxvWDNaVmRWZGZWMjlwUTFrd2QyYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c586c556db03:0x65b1097ff1088a2a"}, {"name": "places/ChIJA9tWxYbFwoARKooI8X8JsWU/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pFNFRuaGFhblpUT1U1b2NuSTFSV3gxVjNsdmFHYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "This is my second time ordering, and the quality is consistently great! Everything tastes fresh, delicious, and healthy. I especially love their sugar free yogurt.It’s light, refreshing, and guilt-free. Highly recommend!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This is my second time ordering, and the quality is consistently great! Everything tastes fresh, delicious, and healthy. I especially love their sugar free yogurt.It’s light, refreshing, and guilt-free. Highly recommend!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "shengnan zhang", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111588397130578535172/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.co